msgstr "To bo vstavilo HTML kodo zgoraj, znotraj &lt;HEAD&gt;."

#: application/controllers/admin/preferences.php:272
msgid "Comic Keywords"
msgstr "Ključne besede za strip"

#: application/controllers/admin/preferences.php:278
msgid ""
"By default comic name, tags, parodies and authors will be added inside the "
"&lt;HEAD&gt; as keywords in the main comic page. If you'd like to have other"
" custom keywords, write them there. Note that each keyword must be separated"
" from the others with a comma."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto ime stripa, oznake, parodije in avtorji bodo dodani znotraj "
"&lt;HEAD&gt; kot ključne besede na glavni strani stripa. Če želite imeti "
"druge ključne besede po meri, jih vpišite tja. Upoštevajte, da mora biti "
"vsaka ključna beseda od drugih ločena z vejico."

#: application/controllers/admin/preferences.php:283
