msgid ""
"You need at least PHP version 5.2.0 to run FoOlSlide. This means you have a "
"many years old version. It is suggested to upgrade to a more recent version "
"of PHP to avoid security issues with your server in general."
msgstr ""
"Za zagon FoOlSlide potrebujete vsaj različico PHP 5.2.0. To pomeni, da imate"
" več let staro različico. Predlagamo, da nadgradite na novejšo različico "
