"datoteke. Lahko jo najdete v FoOlSlide prenosu."

#: application/controllers/install.php:328
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The %s directory needs to be writable. Use this command in your shell if "
"possible: %s or change its permissions recursively to 777 with your own FTP "
"software. You won't be able to install or run FoOlSlide without this."
msgstr ""
"Imenik %s mora biti zapisljiv. Uporabite ta ukaz v vaši lupini, če je to "
"mogoče: %s ali zamenjajte dovoljenja imenika rekurzivno v 777 z vašo FTP "
"programsko opremo. Brez tega ne boste mogli namestiti ali pognati FoOlSlide."

#: application/controllers/install.php:335
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The %s directory needs to be writable as well. Use this command in your "
"shell if possible: %s or change its permissions recursively to 777 with your"
" own FTP software. You won't be able to install or run FoOlSlide without "
"this."
msgstr ""
"Imenik %s mora biti prav tako zapisljiv. Uporabite ta ukaz v vaši lupini, če"
" je to mogoče: %s ali zamenjajte dovoljenja imenika rekurzivno v 777 z vašo "
"FTP programsko opremo. Brez tega ne boste mogli namestiti ali pognati "
"FoOlSlide."

