"posodobitve. Če je mogoče, uporabite ta ukaz v lupini: %s"

#: application/controllers/install.php:363
#: application/models/upgrade_model.php:155
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The %s directory would be better if writable, in order to deliver automatic "
"updates.<br/>It was impossible to determine the user running PHP. Use this "
