#: application/views/admin/loadbalancer/balancers_list.php:7
msgid ""
"FoOlSlide load balancers are servers that serve images cloned from the "
"master server. You can host a load balancer by either using an external "
"service (like a Content Delivery Network), or use another FoOlSlide "
"installation in \"client mode\" on another server."
msgstr ""
"Izravnalniki obremenitve FoOlSlide so strežniki, ki strežejo slike, "
"klonirane iz glavnega strežnika. Izravnalnik obremenitve lahko gostite tako,"
" da uporabite zunanjo storitev (kot je omrežje za dostavo vsebine) ali "
"uporabite drugo namestitev FoOlSlide v \"odjemalskem načinu\" na drugem "
"strežniku."

#: application/views/admin/loadbalancer/balancers_list.php:9
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The process of setting up a FoOlSlide Balancer is very simple: you just "
"install a slide on the other server, provide it with the URL to this slide "
"(%s), and add the URL for the other slide below. The rest is automatic."
msgstr ""
"Postopek nastavitve FoOlSlide Balancerja je zelo preprost: preprosto "
"namestite diapozitiv na drugi strežnik, mu zagotovite URL tega diapozitiva "
"(%s) in spodaj dodate URL za drugi diapozitiv. Ostalo je samodejno."

#: application/views/admin/loadbalancer/balancers_list.php:11
msgid ""
"The percentages are for ease and you can set each host to any percentage. "
"For example, if you set two load balancers at 100%, they will actually "
"operate at 50% each."
msgstr ""
"Odstotki so za lažjo uporabo in vsakemu gostitelju lahko nastavite poljuben "
"odstotek. Na primer, če nastavite dva izravnalnika obremenitve na 100 %, "
"bosta dejansko delovala pri 50% each."

#: application/views/admin/loadbalancer/balancers_list.php:13
msgid ""
"Currently, the load balancer does not support serving downloadable "
"compressed archives. These will be served by the master FoOlSlide "
"installation instead. Please keep this in mind while you are distributing "
"the percentages."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno izravnalnik obremenitve ne podpira streženja stisnjenih arhivov, ki"
" jih je mogoče prenesti. Te bo namesto tega stregla glavna namestitev "
"FoOlSlide. Upoštevajte to, ko razdeljujete odstotke."

